***story***
once opon  a time,in a forest, there lived a  monkey who resided on a berry tree, which was on the bamks of a river.
in the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife....
one day the rocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.
the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruits.
the crocodile came back for some more fruits as he loved them.
as day passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became friends.